b_paragraph\" ><strong>- Buy fruits, syrups and other ingredients to make ice cream.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Bring ingredients to discover and unlock different flavors.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Make more money by selling complex recipes that you can create in your ice cream lab.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Increase the level of your business to unlock more stuff about your truck.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165030/extras/a1d706da4b1681e5133c9d25b8452c75.poster.avif?t=1766696848\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165030/extras/a1d706da4b1681e5133c9d25b8452c75.webm?t=1766696848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165030/extras/a1d706da4b1681e5133c9d25b8452c75.mp4?t=1766696848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165030/extras/49e6da2eba06ceed8a1a3bc9825a8d7e.avif?t=1766696848\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165030/extras_big/49e6da2eba06ceed8a1a3bc9825a8d7e.avif?t=1766696848 width=800 height=591 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                                    ENJOY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the 